## AWS Organizations vs IAM

| AWS Organizations | IAM |
|-------------------|-----|
| Manage multiple AWS accounts | Manage users and permissions within one account |
| Centralized governance | Identity and access management |
| Consolidated billing | User authentication and authorization |

---

## AWS Organizations vs AWS Identity Center

| AWS Organizations | AWS Identity Center |
|-------------------|--------------------|
| Manage AWS accounts | Single Sign-On (SSO) for users |
| Billing & governance | User login management |
| Service Control Policies | Permission sets |

